Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:30.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Was Suou really here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:34.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but she went somewhere else with Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:36.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:39.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, to meet Izanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:42.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you stop her even though you knew that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:44.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If Izanami and Izanagi meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:47.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,...the prophecy will come true and the world will be ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:48.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:52.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There are times when you must meet, regardless of the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:54.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:56.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, I haven’t told you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:58.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:02.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,but before that, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.67,0:03:04.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They’ve found this place, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is my remuneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:48.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it from the girl called Youko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:54.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That your true goal is to prevent the prophecy from coming true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:57.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:02.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill Izanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Hazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:10.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't kill Youko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:20.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nobody's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:27.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Did Youko lie to me, even though I was so nice to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:34.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shizume did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:37.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He put her body into the ME Squeezer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:41.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and analyzed the data up until her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:42.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:47.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He’s joined the CIA and betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:50.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, the outside of the Gate is surrounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:57.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and every international agency in PANDORA, including us, is under their authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:06.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Please go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:09.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of the traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,BK201.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Izanami is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:38.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.18,0:05:46.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you taking us now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:48.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:49.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:52.72,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,July went to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:54.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Her? You mean Suou?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:57.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, because this is the Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:00.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A place where all your wishes come true, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:01.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We're going. Hold tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:12.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We've lost Alpha team's signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:15.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,"Defeat your enemies using one of their own."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up with the squeezing process!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:22.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Find out from the professor's memories where they're heading to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:49.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's an empty shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:55.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Her soul has already awakened and is heading to the center of the Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:59.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Only her empty shell is lying there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:02.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We were too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:06.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And so were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:16.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is where Professor Pavlichenko and I built the supercomputer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:24.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:26.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No, Shion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:31.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they look like Shion, but these specimens aren't even dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:35.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:39.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,All the memories of the world recorded by the doll network,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:45.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and all the memories of mankind from the ME network are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:49.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:52.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see it any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:56.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I bet everything I had on Shion-kun's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:08:05.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,For that, we tricked MI-6 and CIA to make them force Shion and the professor out of Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:10.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:16.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That there is proof of mankind's existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:20.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion-kun copied it by using his powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:22.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,An alternate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:27.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I heard everything from Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:32.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That I was born two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:36.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And how my memories were created by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:39.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you like my present?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:44.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't have that memory, perhaps I wouldn't be here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:47.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That memory was also my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:52.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I always dreamed of going back to that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:55.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and I realized that you wanted the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:57.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:04.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I just injected it by thinking it was a normal, human-like memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:10.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It would have been awkward to release you into society without a memory like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:14.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That is not my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:23.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you've become a contractor, you perceive your surroundings with your emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:26.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:29.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Contractors don't think like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:31.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,At least, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:37.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I was influenced by the friends I've been traveling with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:44.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That very word is alien to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm not one either?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Am I-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:51.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:54.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Because to me you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:58.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:10:00.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Izanami forced him to commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:01.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So Izanami did that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:11.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:13.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:16.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion! Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:25.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She stopped her awakening by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:31.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:36.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,On the day we retrieved her, we were planning to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:43.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But on that very day, her reactions as Izanami stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:48.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Aware of her powers should she awaken, we hurried and sealed her with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:52.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Until you destroyed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:58.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We hoped that she would go back to sleep on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:01.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But that miracle didn't occur again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:04.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not blaming you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:09.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind had no chance in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:14.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since the Gates appeared on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:16.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:21.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:24.95,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Episode 12    The Ark of the Star
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you? Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,July?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:46.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, go straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.72,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:03.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:05.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:09.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The mission's been aborted. Go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:15.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The higher-ups made an agreement with America not to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:16.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I won't come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:22.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I like being with Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,An evolving doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:28.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:30.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:39.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,July!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:46.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't Mao with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,July?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:54.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:08.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The two of them have met.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:09.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The two of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:12.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Izanami and Izanagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:22.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So it's started, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:31.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, fancy seeing you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:33.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have fun doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:38.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:40.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're that kind of a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:44.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A pervert, just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:56.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Detecting the formation of several dimensional rifts at the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:58.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hell's Gate is opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:01.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Send all troops to the center!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:05.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let them humiliate our country in this matter any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:14.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:17.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:21.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion! Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:24.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The deal is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:27.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your present.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:32.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the world I've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:36.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You’re not making any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:39.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Give my regards to Papa and Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:42.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:44.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion! Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:04.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:06.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I granted his wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:15.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,July!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:41.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hei knew you would become like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:46.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he said he would put an end to this, and left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:51.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,At first I didn't understand what he meant,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:53.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,but now I'm sure he meant this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:16:01.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We promised to put an end to our problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:10.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The meteor core...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:11.51,DTB-Overlap,,0,0,0,,is going to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:22.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,An experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:23.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:28.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There was a problem with our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:33.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we use the ME to input memories into a copied human,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:37.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,those memories wouldn't stay very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:40.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Until we used the meteor core.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:48.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, Suou's very journey was an experiment to make sure her memories wouldn't fade away?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:49.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:53.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So, now that she's lost the meteor core...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:56.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She'll start to lose her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:16:59.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:12.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:20.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:31.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:44.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't erase them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:47.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know of any other Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:52.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you're a copy or not, you're the only Suou I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:55.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They are my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:58.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:01.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't erase them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:10.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:14.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You won’t need this where you’re going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:25.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:31.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll always be together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:36.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We can travel again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:40.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:42.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:45.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:48.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hei...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:03.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:12.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:16.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:24.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:26.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going to Suou?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:30.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if we will make it in time, but if this place is the Gate, my wish will come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:34.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that you will lose something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:36.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stop like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:38.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:41.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,BK201's star...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:13.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:15.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:18.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you should wake up a bit earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:23.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But last night was the best night to see the Gemini meteor cluster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:26.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two! Don't forget your lunches!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:28.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:30.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, your hair is standing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:31.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:33.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How about waking up a bit earlier yourself, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:35.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:41.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:45.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Something is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:49.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder when I started thinking that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:53.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Whether I'm together with my friends, or with my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:58.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I always have the feeling that something is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:03.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,My friends say that I'm longing for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:05.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's not like I'm feeling lonely at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:12.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, I have this reassuring feeling that I’m always protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:20.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,By someone I haven't met or seen yet. Someone I can't even imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:26.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But I have the feeling that I know him very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:32.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And I believe that one day, I'll meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:36.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:50.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's moving away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:54.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's there just like Shion wished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.55,0:21:56.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:58.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,July is with her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.17,0:22:12.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:15.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.74,0:22:17.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.80,0:22:19.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.59,0:22:22.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.69,0:22:26.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I asked you to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.73,0:22:33.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hi! Want a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.90,0:22:41.40,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kureteku yuubae ni senaka osarete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.90,0:22:41.40,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}My back is pressed by the darkening glow of dusk
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:36.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:40.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,After that, we left the Gate as if we were running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.37,0:22:46.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,America took control over the streets of Tokyo to restore their former glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:51.91,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Arukidasu kage ga shimesu hou e
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:51.91,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I start walking toward where my shadow points
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:52.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And the Syndicate operating from the shadows completely ceased to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:23:01.47,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Taenai ikutsu mo no deai to wakare o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:23:01.47,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Repeating the many, ceaseless encounters and partings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:55.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Another Gate has opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.21,0:22:57.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:04.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What is the thing that was prophesied to be born from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.60,0:23:07.65,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kurikaeshi doko e mukau no ka
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.60,0:23:07.65,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Where do I head to?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.40,0:23:12.75,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Hito wa dare mo mayoinagara
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.40,0:23:12.75,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}For all people, while they are lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:14.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And how will it affect the world?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:12.38,0:23:17.51,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}tsumi to iu na no sadame o seotte
Dialogue: 2,0:23:12.38,0:23:17.51,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}they bear the fate known as sin
Dialogue: 3,0:23:17.28,0:23:26.16,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Sore de mo nao ikiru imi o shiru darou
Dialogue: 3,0:23:17.28,0:23:26.16,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Nevertheless, I'll still learn of the meaning to live, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.71,0:23:28.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,In a not so distant future, we chose to walk the same path for the sake of something that's predestined to happen.
Dialogue: 4,0:23:25.98,0:23:31.25,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Bokura wa sou Day by Day
Dialogue: 4,0:23:25.98,0:23:31.25,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}That's right, Day by Day,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.58,0:23:35.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ironically, people called us the Syndicate.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:30.99,0:23:38.20,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ashita e tsuzuku michi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 5,0:23:30.99,0:23:38.20,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}we're midway on the road leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.13,0:23:39.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, I've heard nothing about him.
Dialogue: 6,0:23:37.83,0:23:45.79,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again kimi to futari no mama
Dialogue: 6,0:23:37.83,0:23:45.79,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again, though it'd be great if
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.16,0:23:47.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yet I still believe... that he's alive.
Dialogue: 7,0:23:45.71,0:23:56.08,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}irareta nara ii no ni naa...
Dialogue: 7,0:23:45.71,0:23:56.08,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I could remain together with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.66,0:23:49.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,